longDescription:
Preview: soundcloud.com/tonka3d/sets/total-sound-collection-sound-effects

In this collection you have 260 High Quality Sound Effects, including different themes: House - Domestic / Human - People - Voices / Nature - forest / Places - Background - Ambience / Special - unnatural - creepy / Technology - Interface - Mech / Transportation - vehicles / War - Explosions.

With this collection you can apply sound effects for your architectural or game projects. We also have the Special session, where you have design sounds for your logos and interface screens. The house, nature and places sounds are very special in this collection.

The 260 sound effects were recorded in stereo and some of them digitally manipulated to achieve an even higher quality.
